OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland probably has the
OL,7,Fworst waiting times for cancer
OL,8,Fdiagnosis in western Europe, the
OL,9,Fchairman of Stormont's Health
OL,10,FCommittee has said.
OL,12,FPhilip McGuigan made the remarks as a
OL,13,Fnew report said cancer cases have hit
OL,14,Fa record high in the region with about
OL,15,F10,700 people being diagnosed every
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FA surgeon told MLAs that the issue is
OL,19,Fan "access problem, not a treatment
OL,20,Fproblem".
OL,26,@{D@DOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
