FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FThe report from Cancer Research UK
OL,7,Fsaid more people in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fare being diagnosed with cancer than
OL,9,Fever before ` around 29 new cases
OL,10,Fevery day.
OL,12,FIt found that breast, prostate, lung
OL,13,Fand bowel cancers account for more
OL,14,Fthan half (54%) of new cancer cases in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,17,FThe report also said cancer incidence
OL,18,Frates in Northern Ireland have
OL,19,Fincreased by 14% since the early 1990s.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FCancer Research UK said mortality
OL,7,Frates have decreased over the past 50
OL,8,Fyears, but the number of deaths per
OL,9,Fyear has risen
OL,11,FTheir report said cancer mortality
OL,12,Frates in Northern Ireland are
OL,13,Fcurrently at their lowest recorded
OL,14,Flevel, having fallen by 18% since the
OL,15,Fmid-1970s.
OL,17,FHowever, because of a growing and
OL,18,Fageing population, more people in the
OL,19,Fregion are dying from cancer, with
OL,20,Faround 4,600 deaths every year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FIt said cancer is the leading cause of
OL,7,Fdeath in Northern Ireland, causing 26%
OL,8,Fof all deaths.
OL,10,FProfessor Mark Taylor, who was
OL,11,Fappointed last year as the region's
OL,12,Ffirst regional clinical director for
OL,13,Felective care with a focus on tackling
OL,14,Fthe region's high waiting lists,
OL,15,Fappeared before the Health Committee
OL,16,Fon Thursday.
OL,18,FMr McGuigan raised the new report,
OL,19,Fstating it was "not great reading".
OL,26,@{D@POU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FHe said: "We are still the weakest
OL,7,Fpart of these islands, the weakest
OL,8,Fpart probably of western Europe in
OL,9,Fterms of the longest waits for cancer
OL,10,Fdiagnosis and treatment.
OL,12,F"Only 31% of patients are being
OL,13,Ftreated within 62 days of a red-flag
OL,14,Freferral.
OL,16,F"That's not really great. What is the
OL,17,Ffocus in terms of dealing with red-
OL,18,Fflag referrals."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "Cancer is on the rise
OL,7,Fand that same report talked about a
OL,8,F14% increase, but it also mentioned
OL,9,Foutlook and outcomes have improved.
OL,11,F"It is very important to say this is
OL,12,Fan access problem, not a treatment
OL,13,Fproblem.
OL,15,F"When you get to the clinicians that
OL,16,Fare there to administer the care, I
OL,17,Fstand very proud of the care we give
OL,18,Fto cancer patients as a cancer
OL,19,Fsurgeon."
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,FMcGuigan pointed out that screening
OL,7,Ffor bowel cancer takes place at the
OL,8,Fage of 60 in Northern Ireland, while
OL,9,Fit is at 50 in the rest of the UK and
OL,10,F57 in the Republic of Ireland.
OL,12,FHe said: "We are an outlier in
OL,13,Frelation to that.
OL,15,F"If you can diagnose people earlier,
OL,16,Ftreatment is less complex.
OL,18,F"It would be much more efficient if
OL,19,Fpeople with bowel cancer and all kinds
OL,20,Fof cancer were being screened earlier.
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1777190772
OL,3,CNI 'probably' worst in western Europe
OL,4,Cfor cancer wait times
OL,6,F"How can the department rationalise
OL,7,Fscreening at 60 and not being reduced?"
OL,9,FMr Taylor said: "In bowel cancer,
OL,10,Fthere is absolutely no doubt we are
OL,11,Fbehind our colleagues in the United
OL,12,FKingdom.
OL,14,F"We have a finite budget, we have a
OL,15,Fmassive backlog, we have got to think
OL,16,Fof those earlier diagnostics that
OL,17,Fmight save us money down the line, but
OL,18,Fmore importantly save patients down
OL,19,Fthe line."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@gO]qD@QOUvD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
